title: SOC a mini ocs that runs on Mondays nights (LOOKING FOR ONE MORE PREMADE TEAM!)

embed.description: Teams will be chosen by the first 8 teams that register and meet the criteria. The SumSoc circuit will run very closely to how OCS is. It is great way for your team to gain competitive experience. This also means teams must be organized, prepared and ready!

body:
Hello Summoners
Looking for 1 more team to join the SOC. Its basically a mini OCS that runs on Monday nights. ITS FOR PREMADE teams only. You have to be able to play every monday night and for the 10 weeks roughly. (Start time from 6pm+)
No comfirmed date yet: probably start in 2-3 weeks time.
Have any questions ask below. 
The first team to sign up next and correctly will be given the spot! 
sign up here: https://goo.gl/forms/5FYp6r15vAgnutjJ3
